"title": "1651: numbers, 1–2",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1651: numbers, 1-2",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The number one is often associated with the uniqueness of God and also with the unity between God and his people. The number two is used in a variety of contexts.</p>\n<h2>One</h2>\n<h3>One God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:32\">MRK 12:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4\">DEU 6:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:8\">ISA 44:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa45:21\">ISA 45:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:18\">JHN 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:30\">ROM 3:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:4-1Cor8:6\">1CO 8:4–8:6</a></p>\n<h3>One Father</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:10\">MAL 2:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:9\">MAT 23:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:6\">EPH 4:6</a></p>\n<h3>One Son Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:16\">JHN 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:18\">JHN 3:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:6\">1CO 8:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:2\">2CO 11:2</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:5\">EPH 4:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:17\">HEB 11:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:9\">1JN 4:9</a></p>\n<h3>One Holy Spirit</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:9\">1CO 12:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:11\">1CO 12:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:18\">EPH 2:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:4\">EPH 4:4</a></p>\n<h3>One Saviour</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:10-Isa43:11\">ISA 43:10–43:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:12\">ACT 4:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5\">1TI 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>One Shepherd</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:11\">ECC 12:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek34:23\">EZK 34:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:22\">EZK 37:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:24\">EZK 37:24</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:16\">JHN 10:16</a></p>\n<h3>One faith</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">JUD 1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:8-Gal1:9\">GAL 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:5\">EPH 4:5</a></p>\n<h3>One sacrifice for sin</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:27\">HEB 7:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:10\">ROM 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:12\">HEB 9:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:28\">HEB 9:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:10\">HEB 10:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18\">1PE 3:18</a></p>\n<h3>One who acts on behalf of others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:50\">JHN 11:50</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:8-1Sam17:10\">1SA 17:8–17:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:14\">JHN 18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:15-Rom5:19\">ROM 5:15–5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim2:5\">1TI 2:5</a></p>\n<h3>One people of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:22\">EZK 37:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:4-Rom12:5\">ROM 12:4–12:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:17\">1CO 10:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:12-1Cor12:13\">1CO 12:12–12:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:16\">EPH 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:6\">EPH 3:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:4\">EPH 4:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">COL 3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Christians are to be one in Jesus Christ Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:21\">JHN 17:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:28\">GAL 3:28</a></p>\n<h3>Christians are to be one in spirit</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:2\">PHP 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:6\">ROM 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor13:11\">2CO 13:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a></p>\n<h3>Married couples become one flesh</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:24\">GEN 2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:5\">MAT 19:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:8\">MRK 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:16\">1CO 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:31\">EPH 5:31</a></p>\n<h3>One priority for all people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:28-Mark12:30\">MRK 12:28–12:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:36-Matt22:37\">MAT 22:36–22:37</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:4-Deut6:5\">DEU 6:4–6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:42\">LUK 10:42</a></p>\n<h2>Two</h2>\n<h3>Two of every kind in the ark</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:19-Gen6:20\">GEN 6:19–6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen7:2\">GEN 7:2</a></p>\n<h3>Two brothers</h3>\n<p>Isaac and Ishmael:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:17-Gen17:19\">GEN 17:17–17:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:10\">GEN 21:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:9\">GEN 25:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen25:23\">GEN 25:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:10-Rom9:13\">ROM 9:10–9:13</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:1-Gen48:20\">GEN 48:1–48:20</a> <em>Ephraim and Manasseh</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:18-Matt4:22\">MAT 4:18–4:22</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:16-Mark1:20\">MRK 1:16–1:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:10\">LUK 5:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:40-John1:42\">JHN 1:40–1:42</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:11\">LUK 15:11</a> <em>the prodigal son and his brother</em></p>\n<h3>Two wives</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:3\">GEN 16:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut21:15\">DEU 21:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:2-1Sam1:7\">1SA 1:2–1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam27:3\">1SA 27:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:5\">1SA 30:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:18\">1SA 30:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam2:2\">2SA 2:2</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr24:3\">2CH 24:3</a></p>\n<h3>Teams of two: Jesus Christ's disciples</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:1\">LUK 10:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt21:1\">MAT 21:1</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:1\">MRK 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:29\">LUK 19:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:13\">MRK 14:13</a></p>\n<h3>Teams of two: Paul and his colleagues</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:42-Acts13:50\">ACT 13:42–13:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:1-Acts14:3\">ACT 14:1–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:12\">ACT 15:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:22\">ACT 15:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:19-Acts16:40\">ACT 16:19–16:40</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:10\">ACT 17:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:1\">1CO 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:1\">2CO 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:1\">PHP 1:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:1\">COL 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>Two tablets of the Ten Commandments</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod31:18\">EXO 31:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:29\">EXO 34:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:15\">DEU 9:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut9:17\">DEU 9:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:3\">DEU 10:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr5:10\">2CH 5:10</a></p>\n<h3>Two cherubim</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:18\">EXO 25:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:22\">EXO 25:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod37:7\">EXO 37:7</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num7:89\">NUM 7:89</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs6:25\">1KI 6:25</a></p>",
